title: [Icemule Historical Society]
description: Rows of smoke-yellowed oil paintings portraying distinguished halflings line either side of this long, narrow room.  At the far end a broad desk topped with dusty green leather sits in a pool of dim light.  The half-round window above is tinted a very pale blue.

Rows of smoke-yellowed oil paintings portraying distinguished halflings line either side of this long, narrow room.  At the far end a broad desk topped with dusty green leather sits in a pool of silvery moonlight.  The half-round window above is tinted a very pale blue.
